casebody.data:
PEOPLE
v.
AMERICAN CONTRACTORS INDEMNITY COMPANY. No. S219842. Supreme Court of California March 23, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, and CUÉLLAR, JJ., concur.

Dismissed and remanded to CA 1/1. Review in the above-captioned matter, which was granted and held for People v. Safety National Casualty Corp. (2016) 62 Cal.4th 703, 199 Cal.Rptr.3d 272, 366 P.3d 57, is hereby dismissed. (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(b)(1).)

KRUGER, J., was absent and did not participate.
